name: Titanic
description: Historic gay club established in 1982, especially popular with bears, leather lovers, and butch aesthetics. Underground club specializing in masculine-themed parties with bold, unapologetic atmosphere and body-positive environment. Hosts monthly Pitbull events.

name: Travel Shack
description: Vibrant bar in Funfhaus district hosting daily events including Crazy Karaoke Nights (Tue, Fri, Sat) and Pub Quizzes (Wed). Features 4 rooms: play room with table football and billiard, american bar, dancing room and karaoke room.

name: Tunnel
description: Restaurant and jazz club in Josefstadt, typical student meeting point. Open every evening with jam sessions on Mondays. Features live music and casual dining atmosphere.

name: U4 Discotheque
description: Cult venue opened in 1980, named after nearby U4 subway line. One of Vienna's most legendary nightlife venues that has hosted many international celebrities. Entry from age 18.

name: Vie i Pee
description: Vienna's first true hip-hop club since 2015, hosting around 500 guests. Features soul, funk, jazz, R'n'B, rap and hip hop. Includes spacious 1400m² garden with lounge and wooden terrace. Accessible via U2 Messe-Prater.

name: Viper Room
description: Club in Landstraße focusing on underground metal scene with capacity of 300 people. Has garnered cult following over the years. Accessible via U3/U4 Wien Landstraße or U3 Rochusgasse.

name: Volksgarten Club Disco
description: Disco in Vienna city centre in middle of beautiful garden. Accessible by U2 Museumsquartier, U2/U3 Volkstheater, or Tram 1, 2, D Burgring. Music mainly house, disco and party hits.

name: Volksgarten Pavillon
description: Summer venue with 1950s architecture transforming from daytime café to evening party spot. Famous for 'Das Techno Café' every Tuesday night since 1996. Also hosts 'Fruity Hop' and 'The Birds & The Bees' themed evenings with queer crowds.

name: Weberknecht
description: Club, lounge, and live music venue with up to four floors featuring best parties in Vienna. Features 2 large lounge areas and two outdoor areas with garden. Music styles include alternative, rock, metal, techno, and karaoke.

name: Wirr
description: Venue requiring additional research - web search limit reached. Located in Vienna.
